  "title": "Cannot fetch value from the attributeName which is in hierarchical level",
  "body": "I am having a hierarchical object in json. I am using **connectMenu** to list out the catogories in a dropdown. When I give **attributeName: \"taxonomies_hierarchical.category.lvl0\"** i got response. But When I give **attributeName: \"taxonomies_hierarchical.category.lvl1\"**, the result is empty. How can I get the **lvl1** values?\r\n\r\n```\r\n\"taxonomies_hierarchical\": {\r\n        \"category\": {\r\n          \"lvl0\": [\r\n            \"Manchester\"\r\n          ],\r\n          \"lvl1\": [\r\n            \"Manchester > Hopwood House\"\r\n          ]\r\n        }\r\n}\r\n```",
